x; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 0px none rgb(10, 10, 10);&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 500; margin: 0px; text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 0px none rgb(10, 10, 10);&quot;&gt;text&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;pCTyYe&quot; dir=&quot;ltr&quot; data-copy-service-computed-style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; margin: 0px; text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 0px none rgb(10, 10, 10);&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; margin: 0px; text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 0px none rgb(10, 10, 10);&quot;&gt;&lt;pre data-copy-service-computed-style=&quot;font-family: monospace; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; margin: 14px 0px; text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 0px none rgb(10, 10, 10);&quot; style=&quot;font-family: monospace; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; margin: 14px 0px; text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 0px none rgb(10, 10, 10);&quot;&gt;&lt;code data-copy-service-computed-style=&quot;font-family: monospace; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; margin: 0px; text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 0px none rgb(10, 10, 10);&quot; style=&quot;font-family: monospace; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; margin: 0px; text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 0px none rgb(10, 10, 10);&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;undefined&quot; data-copy-service-computed-style=&quot;font-family: monospace; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; margin: 0px; text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 0px none rgb(10, 10, 10);&quot; style=&quot;font-family: monospace; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; margin: 0px; text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 0px none rgb(10, 10, 10);&quot;&gt;[ Data Sources ] ──► ( Ingestion via Power Query Ribbon )&#xa;                            │&#xa;                            ▼&#xa;               ┌──────────────────────────┐&#xa;               │    Power Query Online    │&#xa;               │  ┌────────────────────┐  │&#xa;               │  │   Diagram View     │  │ ◄── (Tracks Lineage visually)&#xa;               │  └─────────┬──────────┘  │&#xa;               │            ▼             │&#xa;               │  ┌────────────────────┐  │&#xa;               │  │  Data Preview &amp;amp;    │  │ ◄── (Manipulate columns &amp;amp;&#xa;               │  │  Applied Steps     │  │      generate M Code)&#xa;               │  └─────────┬──────────┘  │&#xa;               └────────────┼─────────────┘&#xa;                            ▼&#xa;                 [ Native Fabric Storage ]&#xa;               ( Lakehouse / Warehouse / SQL )&#xa;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;LIBz9e&quot; data-animation-atomic=&quot;&quot; data-sae=&quot;&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; margin: 3px 0px 0px; text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(240, 242, 245);&quot; data-copy-service-computed-style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 400; margin: 3px 0px 0px; text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(240, 242, 245);&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;P8PNlb&quot; data-copy-service-computed-style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 400; margin: 0px; text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 0px none rgb(10, 10, 10);&quot; style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans&amp;quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 400; margin: 0px; text-decoration: none; border-bottom: 0px none rgb(10, 10, 10);&quot;&gt;Use code with caution.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span data-ved=&quot;2ahUKEwjAw6T05pCVAxWMXUEAHb1bBTkQopQPegYIAAgEEAE&quot; data-copy-service-computed-style=&quot;font-family: &amp;quot;Google Sans